        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="5">
            <sentence id="5.1">While the Apache Group has claimed that Apache HTTPD 2.0.39 is immune to the 
apache-scalp.</sentence>
            <sentence id="5.2">c exploit, users on several mailing lists say that these symptoms 
